        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2408834792" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer692220124081879111">This book raises some interesting subjects for discussion. The short stories are just wonderful. I wondered if the auther was suggesting that it might not be possible for black and white communities ever to understand and accept each other. Some divide separates us that lies just eyond our comprehension. A very good read.</span>

          </span>
